/div>\n<div class=\"custom_html itineary-boxess itinerary rr\">\n<div class=\"panel-heading includ-title-div\">\n<h3 class=\"panel-title includ-title\">FAQs for Shimla Packages<\/h3>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> Which Is The Best Time To Visit Shimla?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> Summer is the most preferred time to visit Shimla as the weather stays quite pleasing and favorable in the summer months. Winter is also a good time if you are excited to witness the snowfall and want to enjoy ice-skating.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> How Far Is Kufri From Shimla?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> Kufri is only at a distance of 15 km from Shimla and it takes 45 minutes to cover the road distance between the two destinations.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> Which Is The Nearest Airport To Shimla?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> Jubbarhatti Airport is the nearest airport but it is not operational in all the seasons and is not on the regular route of commercial airlines. Hence, if you are coming by flight then take book a flight to Chandigarh Airport.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> When Does Snowfall Start?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> If you are looking for snowfall in Shimla then plan your trip at the end of December or in January.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> Is It Safe To Travel Shimla By Train?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> Yes, you can easily reach Shimla by train through Kalka-Shimla rail line.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> How Many Days Are Enough for Shimla Tour?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> A week-long trip would be enough to explore the wonders of Shimla and enjoy the activities.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> How Far Is Shimla From Chandigarh?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> Chandigarh is located at a distance of only 130 km from Shimla and it takes you almost 4 hours to cover the road distance between the two cities.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> Is Shimla A Very Economical Holiday Destination?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> Shimla is a reasonably priced holiday site but during the peak season you might have to spend little extra money on hotels and transport.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> Can We Plan A Family Trip To Shimla?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> Yes, you should definitely plan a family trip to Shimla to spend some quality time with them.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> What Are Some Of The Best Places In Shimla For Accommodation?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> You will find multiple of options to accommodate yourself in the city as there are plenty of hotels established and depending upon your budget you can select the best one. The price varies from hotels to hotels and the amenities and service provided by them.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div itemscope=\"\">\n<div class=\"click_ques\" itemprop=\"name\"><span>Q.<\/span> Is There Any Travel Tip To Follow While Exploring Shimla?<\/div>\n<div class=\"ans_sec\" style=\"overflow: hidden; display: none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p><span>A.<\/span> As you are traveling to a new place, so you need to be very vigilant and attentive towards your luggage. Don\u2019t try to be overfriendly with the strangers as this might trap you in any problem. You are also advised not to eat any raw or cut fruits from outside and try eating foods from a decent place and always drink seal-packed mineral water.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"cmsmasters_column one_fourth sidefrBt\">\n<div class=\"cmsmasters_contact_form\">\n<div class=\"wpcf7 no-js\" id=\"wpcf7-f26619-o1\" lang=\"en-US\" dir=\"ltr\" data-wpcf7-id=\"26619\">\n<div class=\"screen-reader-response\"><p role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\"><\/p> <ul><\/ul><\/div>\n<form action=\"\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/10859#wpcf7-f26619-o1\" method=\"post\" class=\"wpcf7-form init\" aria-label=\"Contact form\" novalidate=\"novalidate\" data-status=\"init\">\n<div style=\"display: none;\">\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7\" value=\"26619\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_version\" value=\"6.0\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_locale\" value=\"en_US\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_unit_tag\" value=\"wpcf7-f26619-o1\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_container